===Alternative spellings===
*'''[[sceptic]]''' is mainly used in Britain.

===Noun===
'''skeptic'''
#Someone undecided as to what is true.
#Someone who does not accept beliefs and claims presented by others until they have validated something for himself, requiring strong evidence before accepting any belief or claim.

